Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs36}{\fad(300,300)}我就愛別人去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs36}{\fad(300,300)}無論是誰 無論是誰都愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs36}{\fad(300,300)}大家一起愛他
