Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs36}{\fad(300,300)}愛愛愛愛愛愛愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs36}{\fad(300,300)}愛
